# Video store - Behind the scenes[]

The video store billboards on Pantora in the Star Wars: The Bad Batch episode "Cornered" are not legible in the episode; however, the font and the text at the top has the same design as the one seen on billboards in Star Wars: The Clone Wars, and if you compare them, you can see that it is the same text.
